      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Winds that Burn",
        "Client": "Miserable Man",
        "Description": "As if my life couldn\u0027t get any worse...\r\nI happened upon a spiny Espinas\r\nand before I got fried I managed to\r\nescape...right into the tail-end of\r\na Kushala Daora! Ugh! Can you put\r\nthose beasts out of their misery\r\nbefore they put me out of mine?",
